<!DOCTYPE html>
%html
	%head
		%meta{'content' => "text/html; charset=UTF-8", 'http-equiv' => "Content-Type"}
	%body
		- if @user.first_name.present?
			%p
				== Hi #{@user.first_name},
		
		%p Thanks for wanting to join StreetCred!

		%p You're one step away from joining the team:

		%p= link_to "Click here to claim your profile", "http://www.streetcred.us/participants/search?email=#{@user.email}"
	
		%p Soon you will be on your way to earning recognition for all the good deeds you do across the City.

		%p Thank you for all you do to make Boston great!

		%p - The Street Cred Team

